entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You hope to never meet Darth Vader in person.
entries.journal_entry_description: Darth Vader has warned you for meddling in his affairs.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: [Darth Vader] I will find you, and you will pay for your insolence.
entries.task03_comm_message_text: [Cale Herron] I just heard someone infiltrated the quarantine zone and stole something Vader wanted for the Black Sun. Hahaha...I wouldn't want to be that person right now.
